</strong><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="text-align: justify" class="hsection1" id="n_259">   Святое слово (<i>лат</i>.).<br></br></div> <strong xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">260
