</strong><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="text-align: justify" class="hsection1" id="n_297">   боевая труба (<i>устар</i>.).<br></br></div> <strong xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">298
