</strong><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="text-align: justify" class="hsection1" id="n_304">   Король герольдов (<i>фр</i>.).<br></br></div> <strong xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">305
</strong><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="text-align: justify" class="hsection1" id="n_305">   турнир на копьях (<i>фр</i>.).<br></br></div> <strong xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">306
