</strong><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="text-align: justify" class="hsection1" id="n_329">   охотничий нож (<i>устар</i>.).<br></br></div> <strong xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">330
</strong><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="text-align: justify" class="hsection1" id="n_330">   дружбе (от <i>лат. amicita</i>).<br></br></div> <strong xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">331
</strong><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="text-align: justify" class="hsection1" id="n_331">   Доброго здоровья (<i>лат</i>.).<br></br></div> <strong xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">332
</strong><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="text-align: justify" class="hsection1" id="n_332">   домоправительница, экономка, воспитательница.<br></br></div> <strong xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">333
</strong><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="text-align: justify" class="hsection1" id="n_333">   клетка для зверей (<i>устар</i>.).<br></br></div> <strong xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">334
</strong><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="text-align: justify" class="hsection1" id="n_334">   вассал вассала (<i>лат</i>.).<br></br></div> <strong xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">335
