</strong><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="text-align: justify" class="hsection1" id="n_358">   овраг, лощина (<i>нем</i>.).<br></br></div> <strong xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">359
</strong><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="text-align: justify" class="hsection1" id="n_359">   Заклинание, убивающее насекомых.<br></br></div> <strong xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">360
</strong><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="text-align: justify" class="hsection1" id="n_360">   испарения (<i>устар</i>.).<br></br></div> <strong xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">361
